###### Require administrator privileges ###
RequireAdmin

###### Windows configuration  ###
ActivateWindows
ReplaceLocalAdministrator
DisableWindowsStoreApp        # EnableWindowsStoreApp
DisableFriendlyURLFormat      # UnconfigureFriendlyURLFormat

###### Privacy configurations  ###
DisableInkingAndTypingData    # EnableInkingAndTypingData

###### Hardening Windows  ###
SetDefaultBitLockerAES256     # SetDefaultBitLockerAES128
PutBitlockerShortCutOnDesktop
DisableSSDPdiscovery          # EnableSSDPdiscovery
DisableUniversalPlugAndPlay   # EnableUniversalPlugAndPlay
DisableWinHttpAutoProxySvc    # EnableWinHttpAutoProxySvc

###### Network Functions  ###
DisableIEProxyAutoconfig
DisableMulticastDNS           # EnableMulticastDNS
GetTelemetryBlockingHostfile  # SetDefaultHostsfile

###### Windows Subsystem for Linux  ###
EnableWSL                     # DisableWSL
InstallWSLubuntu1804          # RemoveWSLubuntu1804
InstallWSLdebian              # RemoveWSLdebian
InstallWSLkali                # RemoveWSLkali
InstallWSLFedoraRemix         # RemoveWSLFedoraRemix

###### Operational Tasks  ###
GetWindowsUpdates
CleanLocalWindowsUpdateCache
RunDiskCleanup
# RunSysprepGeneralizeOOBE

###### Install programs  ###
InstallSysmon64
InstallNotepadPlusPlus
Install7Zip
InstallSysinternalsSuite
InstallSpiceGuestTool
InstallGPGwin
InstallThunderbird
InstallOffice365
InstallVisioPro
InstallVMwareWorkstation

###### Browsers and Internet  ###
DisableEdgePagePrediction
InstallFirefox                # RemoveFirefox
CreateFirefoxPreferenceFiles
InstallChrome                 # RemoveChrome
CreateChromePreferenceFiles
CustomizeChrome
InstallOpera                  #

###### Forensic Tools ###
InstallAutopsy

###### Auxiliary Functions  ###
WaitForKey
Restart
